Description
-----------

pmgraph provides "Poor man's" graphics --- a set of extensions to 
the LaTeX picture environment, including a wider range of vectors
and a lot more box frame styles.

Files
-----

pmgraph consists of the following files:
	README
	COPYING
	pmgraph.tex
	pmgraph.sty
	pmgraph.pdf


